div.p:
Denne havebog har forfatteren – der fortæller at han selv har stor erfaring som ”urtegårdsmand” – skrevet fordi der manglede bøger om urtehaver på dansk. ”Jeg haaber, at meninge Mand skal faa Lyst at bruge denne Konst”, erklærer han i sin indledning til læseren.
(26,-15 4to).

The author – who explains that he is a very experienced gardener himself – has written this gardening book because there were not many books on gardening available in Danish. “I hope that ordinary people will be encouraged in the practise of this art”, he tells his reader in the introduction to the book.
(26,-15 4to).
